
# Enable Password
  1. How To Configure Enable Password
      
      Step 1. Router(config)#enable password  YOURPASSWORD
      
 
 #Secret Password
 
   2.Configuration Of Secret Password
   
   Step 1. Router(config)#enable secret  YOURPASSWORD
      
      
      -----------------When Both Secret Password and Enable Password are Configured Then Secret Will Work.-----------.
 
 #Line Console Password.
    
    3.Configuration of Line Console Password
      
     Step 1. Router(config)#line console 0
     Step 2. Router(config-line)password YOURPASSWORD
     Step 3. Router(config-line)login
     
     ---------------By Default Login Is Not Configured.----------------------
